# Marketing API (future)

**Status:** Dormant until `src/app/api/**` routes exist. See `AGENTS.md` → Future Backend.

When activating lead capture or sync endpoints:

## Handler shape

- Thin route handlers; delegate to application modules.
- Zod (or equivalent) validation on all inputs.
- `Cache-Control: no-store` on mutation responses.

## Security

- Rate limiting on public POST endpoints (Redis/Upstash pattern from `onetap-marketing` v1).
- Cloudflare Turnstile verification on public forms.
- Safe client errors; no stack traces or internal ids leaked.
- No PII in logs.

## Privacy

- Privacy Policy link on forms collecting personal data.
- Do not add tracking fields without stated legal basis.

